Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.00,0:00:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning wizarding world. Rita Skeeter here reporting to\Nyou live from the Hogwarts school of witchcraft and wizardry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.96,0:00:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s dawn out here on the Quidditchfield as we prepare to bear witness\Nto the epic battle between PeeWee Gryffindor and Slytherin teams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.70,0:00:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Today dear readers it will decided which team deserves to be remembered\Nas champions and who will forever be disgraced as eternal weenies.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.86,0:00:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why what do we have here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You there! Nerd!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.60,0:00:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you tell us about this gruesome sight, young man?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.66,0:00:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that’s our coach, professor Lupin. It appears he\Nhas killed a beautiful doe in some kind of -- blood lust.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.47,0:00:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Woah! Oh god help me! What the...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...what I kill?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.75,0:00:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning mister Lupin. My name is Rita Skeeter,\NI’m a reporter for the daily prophet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.46,0:00:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.92,0:00:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to explain what’s going on here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.56,0:01:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think everybody is just getting excited for a nice game of Quidditch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.54,0:01:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know my team is ready to go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.05,0:01:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I’m referring to the slaughtered doe and the fact\Nthat your entire person is soaked in blood.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.51,0:01:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.04,0:01:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well ah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.73,0:01:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s tradition!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.08,0:01:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes it’s... it’s tradition that every game before -- before the match,\Nthe -- the Gryffindor PeeWee Quidditch team kill a defenseless doe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.79,0:01:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And devour it! Ah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.41,0:01:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...in – in doing so, we are able to observe the power and ferocity...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.80,0:01:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...of a doe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.45,0:01:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s pretty – that’s pretty cool, ha, Shlongbottom?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.31,0:01:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- That’s Bambi’s mum!\N- Okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.62,0:01:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha. Just eat the doe, Shlongbottom!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn’t!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.64,0:02:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it! Nom nom nom! Nom nom!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.50,0:02:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s good!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.91,0:02:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm Mister Lupin. Mister Lupin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.06,0:02:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s widely rumored that you are engaged\Nin a heated quarrel with a one Severus Snape.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.00,0:02:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you make of the allegations made\Nby professor Snape that you are – and I quote:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.38,0:02:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...unfit to teach children, are a danger to yourself and others,\Nhave never graduated Hogwarts and are a washed up -- looser?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.96,0:02:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- That’s bullshit!\N- Huh!\N- I mean: those are half-trues. Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.39,0:02:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. You can... you can tell Snape that he is a Jerk.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.38,0:02:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can quote me on that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.15,0:02:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear readers. I am starstruck. Entering the scene is\Nnone other than Harry freakin’ Potter the Gryffindor seeker.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.63,0:02:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- How is it hanging, daily prophet?\N- Harry, kid. Good luck on the game, huh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.87,0:03:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it’s time for spectators to take their seats. For what’s\Nshaping up to be a truly remarkable game of Quidditch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rita Skeeter signing off.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.11,0:03:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Severus! What’s the goofiest thing you’ve ever done?\NBecause I bet I just topped it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.18,0:03:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it. My actions led directly to\Nthe death of the only thing I’ve ever loved.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably twice as funny as that. Severus,...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.21,0:03:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just at Hogsmeade treating professor Umbridge the\Ntraditional welcome to Hogwarts body shot, you know?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.81,0:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Of course.\N- And the two of us really hit it off. There was this\Nlittle song, little dance – to make a long story short:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.32,0:03:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- ...we ended up going home together.\N- Oh, headmaster!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Severus, let me finish!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.67,0:03:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So Umbridge slipps out of that hideous outfit and\Nwould you believe it? Professor Umbridge -  get this...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.05,0:03:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- ... is a woman!\N- No!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh yeah!\N- What did you do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, the first thing that came out of my mouth was:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.17,0:03:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhh! [high pitched]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.02,0:03:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I did the only thing that would make\Nthe whole situation less awkward for everybody.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.14,0:03:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- And what’s that?\N-  I disapperated.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.19,0:04:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh yeah.\N- You didn't!\N- I did!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, headmaster! I told you you have to deal with these things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.98,0:04:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s like that one time I made out with professor Grubbly Plank.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She got -- clingy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.69,0:04:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to confront them. Tell them they\Ndon’t have what you’re looking for.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.66,0:04:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Severus, these things just tend to blow over. It was like\Nthat time when everybody was complaining: hey, Dumby.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.72,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to expell Tom Riddle from Hogwarts, ‘cause he’s evil.\NAnd I just told them to stuff it. Eventually everything just worked itself out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that, you know?\N[mobile is ringing]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[???]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god, damn it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.76,0:04:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- It’s a text from Umbridge! It says:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.67,0:04:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to talk. Colon, right parenthesis. Oh!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.29,0:04:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Snape is laughing]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.23,0:04:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I do not envy you!\N[mobile is ringing]\NOh, sorry. That’s me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.81,0:04:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- What the devil?\N- What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.02,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a BBM from Umbridge: "Are you with Dumbledore? Did he get my text?"\NNow you’ve dragged me into this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.47,0:05:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ignore it! Maybe - maybe she’ll just go away.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did you get my text?\N- Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, ye - yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn’t text me back!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you left so quickly last night that I didn’t get a chance to say...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.32,0:05:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, about that, ha ha.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.02,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The last night was the most amazing night of my life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.67,0:05:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh! [high pitched]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.98,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.28,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god, I can’t watch this! Listen, Umbridge.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.10,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The headmaster is terrible with confrontation. What he is\Ntrying to say is that -- well he’s just not that in to you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.35,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.29,0:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You don’t know a god damn thing about our magical\Nnight together, you f***ing little snape in the grass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.14,0:05:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He loves me! He’s the only man who loves me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.05,0:05:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We can be happy. And you’re gonna die!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.03,0:05:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Umbridge, Umbridge, Umbridge, stop! He’s right! He’s - he's right!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t wanna be with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.22,0:06:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only hitting on you because I thought you\Nwere a sexy man. Maybe if you were a man, I --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.60,0:06:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.77,0:06:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m proud to be a woman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m a strong -- woman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.05,0:06:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me smash...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.85,0:06:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Umbridge, I’m sorry! I just made a big goofy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.31,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry if I got your hopes up and I’m sorry if I ran\Naround telling everybody about our sexual exploits.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I only did it because I thought it would make them laugh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they did laugh, a lot!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.96,0:06:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, come on, it’s funny! Ha ha...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.47,0:06:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No what are these?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.29,0:06:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tears? No. Umbridge, you don’t cry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.13,0:06:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Umbridge don’t cry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.69,0:06:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You don’t cry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.87,0:07:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do cry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.02,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You do cry, you chubby little [beep].
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s what I am, just a chubby little [beep].
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.67,0:07:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god, are you crying? Is she crying?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.52,0:07:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s laughing. I mean it is pretty funny. Ha ha ha.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.77,0:07:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Snape and Dumbledore are laughing]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.68,0:07:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.50,0:07:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will destroy you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.54,0:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will grind your bones to make my bread.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.11,0:07:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I will erase everything that you ever were.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will have your job!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.82,0:07:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mark my words, Dumbledore!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.07,0:07:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll have your job! Whaa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.37,0:08:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Severus. Ah, who do you think is going to win the big game, ha?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Gryffindor, sadly.\N- Oh, good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.74,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Draco is such a little shit!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, Lucius!\N- Hey.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.45,0:08:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why Lucius Malfoy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s been a long time, Severus.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah. [both]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.75,0:08:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t expect to see you here. I received a letter saying\Nyou’d be too busy to attend any games this year.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.75,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am, - in a way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.23,0:08:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know how I love Quidditch. I never miss a game!\NEspecially one whose outcome means a great deal to me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.22,0:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes? And what’s so important about this particular Quidditch game?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.04,0:08:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s just say:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.87,0:08:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve made a large wager that weights heavily on the outcome of this game.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.84,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I hope you won’t object. I’ve made\Nsome last minute replacements to your team.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.17,0:08:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Replacements?\N- Yes. Let me introduce you – Yaxley!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.06,0:08:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, coach!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.33,0:08:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are. All new transfers to Hogwarts\Nand all exceptional Quidditch players.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.18,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Now why don’t you run along and tell\Nyour team they’ll be sitting this game out?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish, Lucius.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, boys. Remember:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.84,0:09:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you can to knock Potter off his broom!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure the fall is fatal!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.33,0:09:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- And don’t forget that when we get on that field...\N- [gasp] It’s my Daddy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.67,0:09:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy! Daddy, you came to love me! Woo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Point your toes! [???] chin up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.11,0:09:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad... daddy! Look! I drew you a picture!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s me on the potty!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.41,0:09:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Th..That’s you in the background\Nand you’re saying: that’s my son.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.94,0:09:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the potty, it says: Thank you Draco.\NEven Potties need to eat!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that shading on your hair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Best I’ve ever seen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.05,0:09:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who asked you?\N- You didn't trace this for nothing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.38,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.89,0:09:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Take a look at this, fellows.\NLook at this right here with the paper.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.78,0:10:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is this a cross hatching I detect?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here you cretins!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.62,0:10:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And don’t forget to kill Harry Potter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can I hang on to this?\N-Keep it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.32,0:10:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You listen to me, you little poof.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.93,0:10:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not screw this up! Huh!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t! I won’t, daddy. I won’t!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.50,0:10:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll see you’ll love me after this.\NI’ll catch that snitch. Mark my words!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.07,0:10:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[singing] When I’m on the – hey!
